parameters.text:
=Analyze the following page and extract structured intelligence for the copywriter's brief.

---

URL: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json.referenceUrls.url }}

User Description: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json.referenceUrls.description }}

General Campaign Instruction: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json.instructions }}

---

CLEANED PAGE CONTENT:

{{ $json.output }}

---

Start by reading the campaign instruction and user description to establish what this page is and what the writer needs from it. Then extract accordingly — prioritize depth where it matters, skip what doesn't serve the brief.

